        descLong: "Function calling lets the LLM decide when and how to call your functions. Define tools with JSON schemas, and the model returns structured tool_call objects with arguments. Your code executes the function and returns results. This enables agents that can search the web, query databases, call APIs, run code, and take actions. Parallel tool calls let the model invoke multiple functions simultaneously. The agentic loop pattern repeats until the model responds without tool calls.",
